nodes.text: Star Wars Builders: Starfighters is a children's activity kit published by Silver Dolphin Books and produced by becker&mayer! on December 20, 2016. The kit includes a 64-page paperback book written by Adam Bray and thick puzzle-like pieces to build three-dimensional models of a T-65B X-wing starfighter and a TIE/ln space superiority starfighter.
